'''努爾丁·贊吉運動'''（{{lang-ar|حركة نور الدين الزنكي}}）是[[敘利亞內戰|敘利亞內戰]]一個反政府[[伊斯蘭主義|伊斯蘭主義]]武裝團體。在2014至15年的時候，它是[[敘利亞革命指揮委員會|敘利亞革命指揮委員會]]的一分子，在期間獲得美國製造的[[BGM-71拖式飛彈|BGM-71拖式飛彈]]。<ref name=tac>{{cite web|url=http://the-arab-chronicle.com/exclusive-18-syrian-revolutionary-factions-advancing-toward-one-army-project/|title=EXCLUSIVE – 18 Syrian revolutionary factions advancing toward a One Army project|work=The Arab Chronicle|accessdate=2014-09-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826115620/http://the-arab-chronicle.com/exclusive-18-syrian-revolutionary-factions-advancing-toward-one-army-project/|archivedate=2014-08-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2014年，努爾丁·贊吉運動是[[阿勒頗|阿勒頗]]最有影響力的武裝派系之一。<ref name=crisis>{{cite web|url=http://www.crisisgroup.org/~/media/Files/Middle%20East%20North%20Africa/Iraq%20Syria%20Lebanon/Syria/155-rigged-cars-and-barrel-bombs-aleppo-and-the-state-of-the-syrian-war.pdf|title=Rigged Cars and Barrel Bombs: Aleppo and the State of the Syrian War|publisher=International Crisis Group|date=2014-09-09|accessdate=2014-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140911154740/http://www.crisisgroup.org/~/media/Files/Middle%20East%20North%20Africa/Iraq%20Syria%20Lebanon/Syria/155-rigged-cars-and-barrel-bombs-aleppo-and-the-state-of-the-syrian-war.pdf|archive-date=2014-09-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==歷史==
努爾丁·贊吉運動於2011年成立。

2014年12月，贊吉運動加入由其它在阿勒頗行動的伊斯蘭主義反政府武裝組成的[[沙姆陣線|沙姆陣線]]聯盟。<ref name=levantfront>{{Cite news|title=The Levant Front: Can Aleppo’s Rebels Unite?|url=http://carnegieendowment.org/syriaincrisis/?fa=57605|date=2014-12-26|accessdate=2015-03-09|publisher=Carnegie Endowment for International Peace|archive-date=2014-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141226221548/http://carnegieendowment.org/syriaincrisis/?fa=57605|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年5月6日，贊吉運動加入由其它在阿勒頗的反政府武裝組成的[[征服阿勒頗|征服阿勒頗]]聯合行動室。<ref>Jennifer Cafarella; Genevieve Casagrande (7 October 2015). ''[http://www.understandingwar.org/sites/default/files/Syrian%20Opposition%20Guide_0.pdf Syrian Opposition Guide] {{Wayback|url=http://www.understandingwar.org/sites/default/files/Syrian%20Opposition%20Guide_0.pdf |date=20180206120150 }}'' (PDF). Backgrounder. Institute for the Study of War.</ref>

2015年10月19日，有報道稱贊吉運動的軍事指揮官在阿勒頗附近與敘利亞政府軍戰鬥時陣亡。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usnews.com/news/world/articles/2015/10/19/syrian-troops-advance-toward-air-base-besieged-by-is|title=Syrian troops advance toward air base besieged by IS|work=Associated Press|date=2015-10-19|accessdate=2015-10-19|archive-date=2018-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180616204242/https://www.usnews.com/news/world/articles/2015/10/19/syrian-troops-advance-toward-air-base-besieged-by-is|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年7月，網上傳出的影片顯示贊吉運動成員在[[阿勒頗|阿勒頗]]把他們俘獲的一名12歲男童斬首。影片中的人宣稱該男童是親政府民兵[[聖城旅|聖城旅]]成員。<ref name="murder">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-36835678|title=Syria conflict: Rebels 'filmed beheading boy' in Aleppo|author=|work=BBC|date=2016-07-19|accessdate=2017-06-26|archive-date=2016-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161130224431/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-36835678|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Issa">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-36843990|title=Syria conflict: Boy beheaded by rebels 'was fighter'|author=|work=BBC|date=2016-07-21|accessdate=2017-06-26|archive-date=2022-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220117220752/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-36843990|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年9月24日，贊吉運動加入[[征服軍|征服軍]]。<ref name="twitter.com">{{Cite web |url=https://twitter.com/markito0171/status/779628746357805056 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-10-07 |archive-date=2017-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171014131134/https://twitter.com/markito0171/status/779628746357805056 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2017年1月，贊吉運動加入[[沙姆解放組織|沙姆解放組織]]。<ref>[http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/terror-list-omission-1.4114621 Syria's al-Qaeda affiliate escapes from Canada's terror list] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/terror-list-omission-1.4114621 |date=20170706115740 }}. CBC News, 2017-05-15.</ref>

